data.title: Jack Faust by Michael Swanwick HC Avon First Edition (1997)
data.meta_description: Lyrical, arresting and provocative, "Jack Faust" is a cause for celebration -- it is an extraordinary work that entertains gloriously as it takes a deep and disturbing look into the collective soul of humankind.
